        "message": "LU-13606 lnet: Implement MR forwarding\n\nAllow router to queue message while originator is discovered. After\ndiscovery, if both the message originator and the destination are\nmulti-rail, then allow the router to choose a new destination\ninterface.\n\nTest-Parameters: trivial\nSigned-off-by: Chris Horn <chris.horn@hpe.com>\nChange-Id: I828016c9abe45783fdf9845ddc145e73ee1c4144\n"
